---
title: Salmon Cakes with Roasted Sweet Potatoes and Tomato Salad
description: Flaky salmon fillets, crunchy celery, fresh herbs and light panko breadcrumbs come together to create these delicious pan-seared fish cakes. A light mixed salad and roasted sweet potatoes finish off this refreshing meal!
